dc_title_s: Shaded relief aeromagnetic anomaly map of northeastern and east-central Minnesota, M-53
dc_description_s: Aeromagnetic anomaly map, (relative to the earth's magnetic field,  interpretation of magnetic data collected from airborne surveys, the map colors indicate the distribution and concentration of magnetic minerals (primarily iron-bearing) within the upper crust of the earth, shaded-relief (psuedo 3d), northeastern and east-central Minnesota, scale 1:1,000,000.
